{"id": 3029, "genre": 1000, "title": "你觉得「工作」这件事对自己的最大意义是啥？", "description": "不管有没有在工作，你都是怎么看待人类跟工作之间的关系的？（题图来自：iStock ©️ rurquiza）", "record_count": 12143, "comment_count": 25, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20191014234843jktLIB3On2sdJM0V.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 1, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2019-10-14T17:00:00Z", "questions": [{"id": 5965, "title": "你觉得「工作」这件事对自己的最大意义是啥？", "content": "你觉得「工作」这件事对自己的最大意义是啥？", "genre": 2, "options": [{"id": 348301, "content": "避免「因为无事可做而觉得无聊」的空虚感", "image": "img/option/option/201910142235196gjbNVvRi5GaZe8x.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 348303, "content": "获得固定的收入，可以养活自己", "image": "img/option/option/20191014225128VvDEWuN2OdeGhHjB.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 348304, "content": "获得一定的社会地位，或者说在别人眼中的形象", "image": "img/option/option/20191014232207oKx2QyTdk36AwVbZ.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 348305, "content": "能实现一定的价值，不管是对自己还是对别人", "image": "img/option/option/20191014232732fBoYnN0GZR15Ciws.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 348306, "content": "能做自己喜欢做的事 or 用收入支撑自己的爱好", "image": "img/option/option/20191014233617rSqIhXNckUnAl5pK.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 348307, "content": "帮自己维持一点必要的社交，避免彻底跟社会脱节", "image": "img/option/option/20191014233726G0fTSU6PxF2WcHdX.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 348308, "content": "实现其他人（爸妈/对象/亲人）对自己的期待", "image": "img/option/option/201910142341361ZGUdy4JID3tgnlB.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 348298, "content": "我也不确定/不知道，我还没开始工作", "image": "img/option/option/20191014211401WbHnh3ewrfS02tXP.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 348297, "content": "都不是，我觉得工作对我来讲好像没啥意义", "image": "img/option/option/20191014211213a80ktjWMyNKdfoGT.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}]}]}